@subsection Unsetting NAMEREF declarations


@anchor{mbfl_unset_varref}
@deffn {Preprocessor Macro} mbfl_unset_varref (@var{NAME})
The argument @var{NAME} must be the first argument to a previous call to @func{mbfl_local_varref} or
@func{mbfl_global_varref}.  A use of this macro expands into:

@example
unset -v $mbfl_a_variable_@var{NAME}
